{"tid":59871,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《惡魔城》可能拍成劇集","createTime":"2016-12-30T04:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T08:06:52.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d1f9f4faf1a717e466c78f1a05f932343dbf400","tid":59871,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:32:39.000Z","msg":"《惡魔城》無疑是一款非常經典的系列游戲，自該游戲的第一做推出以來，就受到了很多玩家的歡迎。那麼該游戲是否會出動畫呢？相信大家對此肯定也非常關注，日前有小道消息傳來，Adventure Time制作人Fred Seibert公布他將參與一款吸血鬼獵人的改編作品中來，而之前Adi Shaknar也提到過將會在2018年和他合作推出惡魔城劇集。<br />\n<br />\n早在去年Konami就宣布制作惡魔城動畫化的消息。動畫故事將根據 1989 年 KONAMI 在紅白機上發售的系列第三作《惡魔城傳說》改編。主角是貝爾蒙特家族在 15 世紀的唯一后人拉爾夫&middot;貝爾蒙特。動畫將會由曾制作過《探險時光》的弗雷德瑞特工作室制作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.slashfilm.com/castlevania-tv-series/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.slashfilm.com%2Fcastlevania-tv-series%2F&d=2KT%2Fi5ksLszG0e%2B25fHiFJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=d06fcc6c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.slashfilm.com/castlevania-tv-series/</a>"},{"pid":"815aa81072cb098bbc77f8f47f23ee1282a9e479","tid":59871,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪喇屌"},{"pid":"64d17116bf02ea29ef83321c27919ca6b9fe5b6b","tid":59871,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"2d打橫播？"},{"pid":"55ddfe328611641bd106d9e62892309d5782b061","tid":59871,"uid":24512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2d打橫播？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想像到"},{"pid":"161ad09263ddb3b3292218cde63cf50aab21dc83","tid":59871,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2d打橫播？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想像到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src